As a powerful 8th class mage, Ian Paige took countless innocent lives under the orders of Emperor Ragnar, a close friend and ruler of the Greenriver Empire. Yet despite their closeness, Ragnar views Ian as a threat and subsequently poisons him. Using time magic, Ian saves himself and returns 30 years to the past. Now a young boy, Ian joins an elite order of mages to hone his abilities once again. This time, hell get revenge on the emperor who betrayed him and reclaim glory as an 8th class mage!
(Source: Tapas)

There has never been a hero like this before. Is he a hero or an actual demon?
Kang Han-Su was summoned to this world with his classmates. His classmates were amazed by this brand new world and the magic in it, but the only thing Han-Su wanted to do was quickly return home.
Why would I give up my warm, comfortable house to have an adventure in this world?
Even the goddess that summoned me said that if I wasnt willing to, there was nothing she could do to force me and promised to return me to my original world. She did teleport me, but
When I opened my eyes, I was still in this world! All of my friends were gone, and the only thing around me was monsters!!
A goddess tricked me? How do I get back home now? More than that, how do I survive here?!
